Detailed Description

Functions to examine IA-64 instructions.

Availability:
Mode: JIT & Probe
O/S: Linux
CPU: IA-64 architecture

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum LEVEL_BASE::CATEGORY_IPF

Instruction Category abstraction for the IA-64 instruction set.

enum LEVEL_BASE::FCLASS_FLAGS

Options for fclass instruction. See the manual for the meaning of these mnemonics.

To generate these literal values, I wrote an example in the assembler and got the immediate value from pin.log.

enum LEVEL_CORE::INS_PROP_IPF

Properties for IA-64 instructions.

enum LEVEL_BASE::PREDICATE_IPF

Predicate abstraction for IA-64 instructions.

Enumerator:
PREDICATE_ALWAYS_TRUE  Default predication on IA-32 and Intel(R) 64 architectures.
